Montreal to Quebec city by rail.

18:15.728 --> 18:23.728
160 miles of wintry vistas
whipped past the windows,

18:24.671 --> 18:26.572
evocative for some
of another time.

18:26.573 --> 18:29.241
Sturgeon and caviar.

18:29.242 --> 18:33.245
I'm not sure about Dave
McMillan but in Fred's perfect

18:33.246 --> 18:36.248
world we would all
travel by rail.

