18:54.434 --> 18:55.202
Operating manual.

18:55.203 --> 18:56.203
This model train.

18:56.203 --> 18:56.736
Yeah.

18:56.737 --> 19:00.839
So you have other operations.

19:00.840 --> 19:01.708
Yeah.

19:01.709 --> 19:05.777
Books, printed
information, collectibles.

19:05.778 --> 19:07.346
An enduring love for the great

19:07.347 --> 19:08.614
iron horses that still take

19:08.615 --> 19:12.050
passengers across the
frozen land he calls home.

19:12.051 --> 19:15.120
But it is something more
than just nostalgia.

19:15.121 --> 19:18.690
It's also an appreciation
for a dying art.

19:18.691 --> 19:21.527
It's like the old cruise ships.

19:21.528 --> 19:25.264
You transport your comfort.

