We look at the menus of how

19:39.312 --> 19:40.546
people would eat on trains.

19:40.547 --> 19:42.914
It was inspiration of how
we cook in the restaurant.

19:42.915 --> 19:46.452
All the sweet breads and
fresh peas, leg of lamb.

19:46.453 --> 19:47.287
Current jelly.

19:47.288 --> 19:49.455
Very nice pictures in the
dining by train book.

19:49.456 --> 19:51.657
The guy holding the Turkey
and cutting the Turkey.

