It comes from a bottle made out

19:54.327 --> 19:57.229
of glass into a glass
made out of glass right.

19:57.230 --> 19:59.398
Which is kind of cool
in our day and age.

19:59.399 --> 20:02.668
It goes back to
service doesn't it?

20:02.669 --> 20:03.135
Thank you.

20:03.136 --> 20:06.305
We are presented with a
perfectly serviceable omlete.

20:06.306 --> 20:09.074
There may no longer be a smoking

20:09.075 --> 20:11.443
lounge with brass spitoons but

