sense in one way.

32:32.051 --> 32:35.153
I mean, 130 acres produced about

32:35.154 --> 32:36.754
32,000 gallons of maple sap,

32:36.755 --> 32:38.923
which run through these tubes

32:38.924 --> 32:40.225
here where they're cooked down

32:40.226 --> 32:42.527
to about 800 gallons of syrup,

32:42.528 --> 32:46.031
which is more or less what
they use per season here.

32:46.032 --> 32:50.001
Nothing leaves the property.

32:50.002 --> 32:51.269
